<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Overview">Overview</span></h2>
<p>One of the most dangerous ships in its class, the PX is quick, tough and powerful. It has a large laser generator, one more weapon slot in its main than the <a href="/index.php/Argon" title="Argon">Argon</a> <a href="/index.php/Heavy_Centaur" title="Heavy Centaur">Heavy Centaur</a> and <a href="/index.php/Boron" title="Boron">Boron</a> <a href="/index.php/Heavy_Hydra" title="Heavy Hydra">Heavy Hydra</a>, and boasts <a href="/index.php/Pulsed_Beam_Emitter" title="Pulsed Beam Emitter">Pulsed Beam Emitter</a> capable turrets with enviable coverage. Its appearance is similar to the <a href="/index.php/Xenon_P" title="Xenon P">Xenon P</a>, but it has more engines and a slightly larger hull. Its huge agility advantage is lost however, and it is more in line with its fellow <a href="/index.php/M6%2B" title="M6+">M6+es</a>.
</p>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Background">Background</span></h2>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Physical_Characteristics">Physical Characteristics</span></h2>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Combat"> Combat </span></h2>
<p>A dangerous foe, the PX is rarely encountered alone, generally found at the head of scouting parties or protecting <a href="/index.php/Xenon" title="Xenon">Xenon</a> capital craft. It should be avoided by light and medium fighters, and combated with extreme caution by heavy fighters and other corvettes. Its PBE turrets will shred anything trying to find a blindspot and its lethal main array will obliterate anything in front of it. Best fought at either long range or, in the case of other corvettes, very close range assuming the pilot is confident they can remain behind it. 
</p><p>If you are lucky enough to capture one, they are useful in escort or player ship roles, as the AI should never be left unescorted.
</p>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Equipment"> Equipment </span></h2>
<p>One of the few <a href="/index.php/M6" title="M6">M6</a> ships that can effectively use the mid-level weapons like the <a href="/index.php/Ion_Shard_Railgun" title="Ion Shard Railgun">Ion Shard Railgun</a> due to its good laser generator. Uses 4x200Mj shields.
</p>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Availability"> Availability </span></h2>
<p>Board only - very difficult.
</p>
